インタフェース BooleanCompution

すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
BooleanGettable, BooleanObservable, Compution<java.lang.Boolean>, Gettable<java.lang.Boolean>, Observable<java.lang.Boolean>, java.io.Serializable
既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
ComparativeCompution, LogicalCompution
public interface BooleanCompution
extends Compution<java.lang.Boolean>, BooleanGettable, BooleanObservable
Boolean value compution, includes Getter and Observer.

NOT includes Setter.

This instance is built from other Property or Compution.

  • To get value, BooleanGettable.booleanValue()
  • To detect value changed, Observable.addChangeListener(ChangeListener)
  • To wait until condition is true,
    • BooleanObservable.waitUntil(boolean)
    • BooleanObservable.waitUntil(boolean, long, java.util.concurrent.TimeUnit)
  • To logical-compute,
    • BooleanObservable.and(BooleanObservable)
    • BooleanObservable.or(BooleanObservable)
    • BooleanObservable.not()
    • BooleanObservable.xor(BooleanObservable)
    • BooleanObservable.nand(BooleanObservable)
    • BooleanObservable.nor(BooleanObservable)
関連項目:
Boolean, BooleanGettable, BooleanObservable, Compution, BooleanProperty
